name: How to Make an NFT - UNDER CONSTRUCTION
description:
I created an entire "fansite" for the blockchain, inspired by web design circa 1995. I loved the dichotomy between very modern technology, and the early internet. I tried to capture every detail and nuance of that time period. Who can forget Under Construction pages?! 

If people enjoy the project, I will post more of the website, including the Guestbook. We are still arguing with strangers online almost 3 decades later!
